Elmore Leonard Obituary (Sadly)

LEONARD ELMORE J. age 87, August 20, 2013. Dear father of Jane (Gary) Jones, Peter (Julie) Leonard, Christopher (Suzy) Leonard, Bill (Carmen) Leonard, and Katy (Jim) Dudley. Cherished grandfather of Shannon (John) Belmont, Tiffany Jones, Megan (Brett) Johnston, Tim Leonard, Alex Leonard, Max Leonard, Ben Leonard, Hillary Leonard, Kate Leonard, Abby Leonard, Joe Dudley, Nick Dudley, and Luke Dudley. Great-grandfather of Jack Belmont, Eliza Belmont, Jane Belmont, Miles Johnston, and Frank Belmont. Also survived by Beverly Decker. Husband of the late Joan Leonard. Brother of the late Margaret Madey. Visitation at Lynch & Sons Funeral Home, 1368 N. Crooks Road (between 14-15 Mile Rds.) Friday 2-8p.m. Funeral Mass at Holy Name Church, 630 Harmon, Birmingham, Saturday 11a.m. Friends may visit at church beginning at 10a.m. Memorials appreciated to Maryknoll Sisters, P.O. Box 317, Maryknoll, New York 10545-0317. Obituary and condolences at lynchfuneraldirectors.com
Lynch Funeral Homepage for Elmore.


